entury German history and thought.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aArts and societyxHistoryx20th centuryxGermany. 0aArts and societyzGermanyxHistoryy20th century. 0aEnlightenmentxGermany. 0aEnlightenmentzGermanyxIntellectual life. 0aEnlightenmentzGermany. 0aJewsxIntellectual lifexGermany. 0aJewszGermanyxIntellectual life. 0aJewszGermany. 7aHISTORY / Europe / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520926257?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520926257423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520926257/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles